              <td style="font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;">Silver</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>120&ndash;139 (60&ndash;69%)</td>
              <td style="color:#059669;font-weight:600;">25%</td>
              <td style="font-weight:600;color:#92400e;">Bronze</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Below 120</td>
              <td style="color:#5c4033;">Merit-based review</td>
              <td style="color:#5c4033;">General</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQs -->
      <div style="max-width:700px;margin:3rem auto 0;">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-center mb-2" style="color:#2d1a0e !important;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-sm mb-6" style="color:#5c4033;">About the IIAT SAT application process</p>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span class="faq-q">Is there any registration fee for IIAT SAT?</span>
            <svg class="faq-chev" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#5c4033" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p>No, IIAT SAT registration is completely free. There are no hidden charges for appearing in the scholarship assessment test. You only pay the tuition fee (minus scholarship) after you decide to enrol.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span class="faq-q">Can I choose my B.Tech branch after the exam?</span>
            <svg class="faq-chev" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#5c4033" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p>Yes. During the counselling session after results, you can indicate your preferred branch from all 6 available B.Tech CSE specialisations. Seats are allotted on a first-come, first-served basis based on your IIAT SAT rank and preference order.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span class="faq-q">What happens if I miss the exam date?</span>
            <svg class="faq-chev" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#5c4033" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p>IIAT SAT is conducted in multiple windows throughout the admission season. If you miss your assigned date, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@iiath.com" style="color:#e34614;font-weight:600;">info@iiath.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+918688664337" style="color:#e34614;font-weight:600;">+91 868 866 4337</a> to request rescheduling, subject to seat availability.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span class="faq-q">Is the IIAT SAT conducted online or offline?</span>
            <svg class="faq-chev" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#5c4033" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p>IIAT SAT is an online proctored exam. You can take it from the comfort of your home using a laptop or desktop with a stable internet connection and a working webcam. No need to travel to an exam centre.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span class="faq-q">Can diploma holders apply?</span>
            <svg class="faq-chev" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#5c4033" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p>Yes, diploma holders in Engineering can apply through the lateral entry pathway. You'll join directly in the 2nd year of the B.Tech programme. The IIAT SAT score still determines your scholarship eligibility.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span class="faq-q">When will I get my scholarship amount confirmed?</span>
            <svg class="faq-chev" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#5c4033" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p>Your scholarship percentage is confirmed along with your IIAT SAT result, typically within 7 working days of the exam. The exact amount is communicated in the offer letter during the counselling process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:3rem;">
        <p style="color:#5c4033;margin-bottom:1rem;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;">Ready to begin your journey?</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.75rem;justify-content:center;">
          <a href="/apply/" class="btn-submit">Register for IIAT SAT &rarr;</a>
          <a href="/iiat-sat/syllabus/" class="btn-submit" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2d1a0e,#5c4033);">View Syllabus</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

